title: Ep - 55 - TOM SCHWARTZ FROM VANDERPUMP RULES
description:
Vanderpump Rules star Tom Schwartz discusses babies, opening his new restaurant with Lisa Vanderpump, and reviews Growing Up Supermodel on Lifetime TV. Comedian Heather McDonald plays Orange County housewife Peggy Sulahian in a round of questions. Matt and Jake from TV Tea Time podcast help Kate review The Challenge Dirty 30 on MTV.
